### Medium Findings

| # | Anti-Pattern | Location | Detail |
|---|---|---|---|
| 4 | **Poor naming** | All 10 tests | Every test is `MethodName_Works` — conveys no scenario or expected outcome. Use `Method_Scenario_ExpectedResult` (e.g., `RemoveProduct_ExistingProduct_IsNoLongerRetrievable`). |
| 5 | **No negative/edge-case tests** | Entire class | Zero tests for: non-existent SKU lookup, `UpdatePrice` on missing SKU (`KeyNotFoundException`), empty search, malformed CSV, duplicate SKU add. These are common production failure paths. |

